{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":27507,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"如果永远不讨论，就永远不可能产生有效的认识","timestamp":1592924280,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":27524,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 但我觉得拿一些片面的甚至修改过的内容出来讨论反而越想越乱，","timestamp":1592924372,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":27525,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"讨论，是为了让更多人想去了解。了解更多，就能慢慢拼出自己完整的价值观和历史观，就能指导实践。","timestamp":1592924379,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":27538,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"键政的目的不在于影响核心的决策，甚至不在于搞清楚核心的决策\n键政的目的在于讨论人间的事情 而不是追捧不可泄露的天机\n键政是精致利己的我们这些普通人用来自我保护的\n（啊 或许其实更多的是打嘴炮过过瘾罢了🤣 谁知道呢","timestamp":1592924446,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":27549,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"满足生理需求","timestamp":1592924488,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":27555,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 138亩地盖成化粪池也不能盖成房子 并不是比我懂更比你懂的顶尖技术人员设计出来的\n大棋观不可取","timestamp":1592924528,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":27557,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 虽然目前尺度收紧，但墙内的政论水平其实反倒提高了，其实很神奇。对岸还有海外阴谋论泛滥已经没法看","timestamp":1592924536,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":27564,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"真理越辩越明呀，况且这本身就是种爱好吧……","timestamp":1592924575,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":27642,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"史观正怕啥键政？不愿键政恰恰是戳中了要害","timestamp":1592925071,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":27702,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 这帽子扣的，不愿意搞键政就是史观不正？","timestamp":1592925756,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":27954,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":4581,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"同一件事老百姓有老百姓的看法，上层有上层的看法，上层因为信息全面当然可能看问题更全面，但是如果老百姓的看法和上层完全脱节了，那也并不是什么好事。键政也是一种反映普通民众政治观点的途径","timestamp":1592927064,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":6,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":4581,"reply":11,"tag":null,"text":"键政的意义是什么？我总觉得我们这些讨论者了解的信息多少也都是一面之词，毕竟我们没站在那个高度看，很多核心的东西我们普通人其实也都不知道，而关于这些决策我们讨论出来的内容又能起到多大的实际意义？\n（单纯发问，没有嘲讽谁的意思）","timestamp":1592924211,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782584,"url":"","vote":{}}}